  "detailed_description": "<strong> Bangman </strong> is a top-down action roguelike in which you have to defeat hordes of bloodthirsty and cute monsters as you travel from world to world. <br><br><i> Embark on an exciting journey to save worlds with our heroes. Many types of weapons and spells will help you with this. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take on the role of one of the summoned heroes and save the worlds from all waves, shooting off crowds of enemies. Each creature contains a useful item that will give you a better chance of survival. At the same time, the enemies are very tenacious and strong, so you think ten times before letting them come to you.<br><br><strong> New heroes </strong> <br><br>Unlock new characters with the help of accumulated gems and get unique abilities and weapons. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Spells </strong> <br><br>Each spell gives you a short-term enhancement of a particular skill / characteristic, increasing your chances of winning!<br><br><strong>Special Skills</strong><br><br>The summoned heroes have their own unique abilities that deal decent damage to enemies. The main thing is to use them wisely, because recovery takes a lot of time, and it can cost you your life!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong> Bangman </strong> is a top-down action roguelike in which you have to defeat hordes of bloodthirsty and cute monsters as you travel from world to world. <br><br><i> Embark on an exciting journey to save worlds with our heroes. Many types of weapons and spells will help you with this. </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/1719334ecd25a4e3aeddaa3585fa579b.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take on the role of one of the summoned heroes and save the worlds from all waves, shooting off crowds of enemies. Each creature contains a useful item that will give you a better chance of survival. At the same time, the enemies are very tenacious and strong, so you think ten times before letting them come to you.<br><br><strong> New heroes </strong> <br><br>Unlock new characters with the help of accumulated gems and get unique abilities and weapons. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/f907f0cd07f155ee5a87d851b4e5bf80.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Spells </strong> <br><br>Each spell gives you a short-term enhancement of a particular skill / characteristic, increasing your chances of winning!<br><br><strong>Special Skills</strong><br><br>The summoned heroes have their own unique abilities that deal decent damage to enemies. The main thing is to use them wisely, because recovery takes a lot of time, and it can cost you your life!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.poster.avif?t=1654195794\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.webm?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811050/extras/fd533017756c2641be0e18e7b78729bb.mp4?t=1654195794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
